snippet.title: [REMIX] Bad Randoms - We Won't Cooperate
snippet.description:
I slightly improved this remix overall, you can hear the better version in my recently published game “Brawl Dash” (Android and iOS) in the level Brawl Ball!)

Or download/listen here:
Download (improved version): https://bit.ly/bad-radnoms_remix_imp
Download (old/this version): https://bit.ly/bad-randoms_remix
Instrumental (old/this version): https://youtu.be/X7_Ot0g30Vo

This one unlike my other remixes won’t be available on Streaming platforms as you can only distribute officially approved remixes there, so for now it will be only here!)

Animation credits of course go to Official Brawl Stars:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCooVYzDxdwTtGYAkcPmOgOw
And some short clips used belong to BLAS:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSQkftbg2z4kz4NNBVs6CIQ
Check his animations if you haven't already, they're great!
